<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ش غ ف<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٨٤٥ - ش غ ف]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شغِفَ/ شغِفَ بـ يَشغَف، شَغَفًا، فهو شَغِف وشَغوف، والمفعول مشغوف<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• شغِفه الحبُّ:</span> شغَفه؛ فتنه وأصاب قلبَه <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{قَدْ شَغِفَهَا حُبًّا}</span> <span class="c4">[ق]</span> "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• شغِف به/ شغِف بحبِّه:</span> أحبَّه وأولع به <span class="c1">"شَغِف بالحريّة- شَغِفٌ بالقراءة- شغوفٌ بالرّياضة"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>